MTN has opened registrations for the iPhone Xs and Xs Max. “MTN will offer Apple’s latest products starting on Friday, 28 September 2018, including iPhone Xs and iPhone Xs Max, the most advanced iPhones ever,” it said. The network added that it will also offer the iPhone Xr. Customers will be able to pre-register for the iPhone Xs and iPhone Xs Max today, and iPhone Xr beginning on 19 October 2018. No pricing information was supplied. Read all about the new iPhones here: